        <h1 class="hero-title">A Complete Ecosystem of<br><span>Structural Excellence</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub" style="font-size:.95rem;margin:16px 0 18px">Because we understand that every structure holds a unique purpose, we have engineered a comprehensively integrated portfolio of construction and design services. Our mission is to provide a seamless, single-point solution that bridges the gap between architectural vision and structural reality.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="pages/our-story.html" class="btn-secondary">Our Story</a>
          <a href="pages/our-team.html" class="btn-secondary">Our Team</a>
